# Assay demo: try → tamper detection

Output docs/assets/demo_try.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 880
Set Height 480
Set Padding 16
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

# Set PATH silently before demo (hidden setup)
Hide
Type "export PATH=/Users/timmymacbookpro/Library/Python/3.9/bin:$PATH"
Enter
Sleep 0.5s
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 0.5s
Show

Type "assay try"
Enter
Sleep 4s

# Let the viewer read the full output
Sleep 5s
